  "description": "Sparse percussive grains scatter across a 6-voice Drift chorus at low rate (0.05 Hz), each grain landing in a slightly different spatial location. The Drift diffusion at 0.72 prevents any single grain from locking to a static position — the scatter never settles. Dry signal is point-source impacts; the Drift makes it a bioluminescent cloud.",
